title: Summoner # 01 (2013) - Jenni Gregory
description: Jayne Sinclair is a Summoner employed by the Metropolitan Constabulary. Along with Detective Gage and his new partner Detective Finnegan she is called to investigate a body found floating in a lake in a city park. Jayne Sinclair is a Summoner. Hers is the ability to summon the spirits of the recently deceased back to the mortal plane. Some spirits resist her call, but others are all too willing to return.
